    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(SN) Anno Domini millesimo CXLV, die mensis madii. Vobis <persName
                            key="#Priors #Monasteries #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3745"
                            >Iohannii</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priors">priori</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Priors #Offersio/donatio #Landed_possessions #Wine"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2420">Sancte Crucis</orgName>, in eundem
                        monasterio Sancte Crucis, ego quidemn <persName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Landed_possessions #Wine #siblingOf"><name
                                ref="Aimo/de Wiperto/de Margnano">Aimus</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name ref="Wibertus">Wiperto</name></persName> de loco
                            <placeName key="#Landed_possessions #Wine #Roads" ref="#places/4107"
                            >Margnano</placeName> offero, in suprascriptam ecclcsiam, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">clausuram unam</rs> cum <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vinea</rs> super se habentem et partim vacua posita in <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/125"><rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/13"
                            >Trivisiensi</placeName></geogName>, pertinenti Margnani; ab uno latere
                        Rodulfinus, ab alio <rs key="#Roads">vie</rs> percurit. Quam autem
                        suprascriptam clausuram cum vinea superdictam, una cum accessionibus et
                        ingressionibus seu cum superioribus et inferioribus suis qualiter superius
                        legitur in integrum, in suprascriptum monasterium ecclesie Sancte Crucis
                        offero, dono, cedo, trado, confero per presentern <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">car(tulam) offersionis</rs> in suprascriptum
                        monasterium ad abendum confirmo, faciendum exinde pars suprascripti
                        monasterii quicquid voluerint sine contradictione suprascripti Aimonis vel
                        eius heredum. Equidem spondeo atque promitto ego qui supra Aimus, una cum
                        meis heredibus suprascripto priori et suprascripto monasterio suisque
                        successoribus ab omni homine defensare seu warentare; quod si defensare non
                        potuerimus vel si vobis exinde quovis ingenio subtrahere quesierimus, tunc
                            <rs key="#Penalty">in duplum</rs> suprascriptam offersionenm et dacionem
                        vobis restituamus, sicut pro tempore fuerit meli[o]rata aut valuerit sub
                        estimatione in consimili loco. Actum in <placeName ref="#places/4108"
                            >Camposion</placeName> ad suprascriptum monasterium. Signum manuum + + +
                        Aimo, hanc cartulam offersionis fieri rogavit. Signum testium + + <persName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Witness"><name ref="Iohannes/de Aimo"
                                >Iohannes</name></persName> de Aimo, <persName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Witness"><name ref="Artvichus/de Margnano"
                                >Artvichus</name></persName> de Margnano, <persName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Witness #siblingOf"><name ref="Adelgerius"
                                >Aldegerius</name></persName> Aimonis <rs key="#siblingOf"
                            >frater</rs>, <persName key="#Offersio/donatio #Witness"><name
                                ref="Ardoinus">Arduinus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Witness"><name ref="Ezelo"
                            >Ezili</name></persName>, <persName key="#Offersio/donatio #Witness"
                                ><name ref="Iohannes/Cagarabia">Iohannes
                        Cagarabia</name></persName>, <persName key="#Offersio/donatio #Witness"
                                ><name ref="Iohannes/de Masnada">Iohannes</name></persName> de
                        Masnada rogati <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs> interfuerunt. (SN) Ego
                            <persName key="#Judge #Notary #Causidicus #Offersio/donatio #Writer"
                                ><name ref="Arnaldus">Arnaldus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> sacri palacii <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Causidicus">causidicus</rs> interfui et <rs key="#Writer"
                            >scripsi</rs>. </ab>
